\c 67 
\m \bd Faarfannaa \bd*\bd 67\bd*
\s2 \bdit \zbr\bdit*Waaqayyoon Barakata Isaatiif Jajuu  (Geggeessituu warra faarfatootaaf; faarfannaa mi'a ribuu qabuun faarfatame; weedduu)
\m \bd 1\bd* Waaqayyo araara nutti haa argisiisu, nu haa eebbisus! Fuula ifaadhaanis nu haa ilaalu!
\m \bd 2\bd* Kanaanis yaa Waaqayyo, karaan ati hojjettu, lafa irratti, fayyisuun kees saba lafa irraa keessatti haa beekamu.
\m \bd 3\bd* Namoonni galata siif haa galchan, yaa Waaqayyo! Namoonni walitti qabaan isaanii galata siif haa galchan!
\m \bd 4\bd* Ati qajeeltootti namoota waan bulchituuf, saba hundumaas lafa irratti waan geggeessituuf, sabni lafa irraa haa gammadu, gammaduu irraa kan ka'es haa faarfatu.
\m \bd 5\bd* Namoonni galata siif haa galchan, yaa Waaqayyo! Namoonni walitti qabaan isaanii galata siif haa galchan!
\m \bd 6\bd* Lafti midhaan baaseera, Waaqayyo gooftaan keenya nu eebbiseera.
\m \bd 7\bd* Waaqayyo nu eebbiseera, andaara lafaa keessa kan jiran hundinuu isa haa sodaatan!
\b 
